column2: Refuel quantity indicator: blank - all tanks.

column2: Refuel valve position indicator light does not come on with valves selected open and refueling manifold pressurized - tank no. 1.

column2: Refueling does not stop at the preselected quantity.

column2: Fuel tank: unwanted fuel transfer from a main tank to the center tank - from tank 2.

column4: Réservoir de carburant : transfert de carburant non souhaité d'un réservoir principal vers le réservoir central - depuis le réservoir 2.
